---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import "@/styles/global.css";
---

<Layout title="Freedom Butchers - About" headerTitle="About Us">
  <main>
    <section
      id="about"
      class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-300 p-10 rounded-lg shadow-xl mb-10 transition-colors duration-300"
    >
      <h2
        class="text-4xl font-extrabold mb-8 text-center tracking-tight text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 underline decoration-wavy decoration-gray-500 dark:decoration-gray-600"
      >
        About Us
      </h2>

      <p class="mb-8 text-lg leading-relaxed text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        At <strong>Freedom Butchers</strong>, we are passionate about providing
        the highest quality meats to our customers. Founded in <strong
          >[Year]</strong
        >, our mission has always been to deliver exceptional products and
        services that meet the needs of our community. We source our meats from
        trusted suppliers who share our commitment to quality and
        sustainability.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
        Our Commitment to Quality
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Quality is our top priority. Every cut of meat we offer is carefully
        selected to ensure that our customers receive only the best. Our
        experienced butchers take pride in their craftsmanship, ensuring that
        every steak, roast, and chop is prepared with care and precision. We
        perform regular quality checks and maintain rigorous standards to ensure
        that our products meet our high expectations.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        We believe that fresh, locally sourced meat not only tastes better but
        is also better for the environment. By partnering with local farms, we
        can offer a selection of meats that are not only fresher but also
        ethically raised.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
        Community Focused
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        At Freedom Butchers, we believe in giving back to the community that
        supports us. From local sponsorships to participating in community
        events, we strive to make a positive impact beyond just providing great
        meats. Our team volunteers regularly at local shelters and food banks,
        providing meals for those in need.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        We also host educational workshops for families and aspiring cooks to
        learn more about meat preparation, cooking techniques, and the
        importance of sustainability in food sourcing. Our aim is to foster a
        stronger connection between our customers and the food they eat.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
        Our Products
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Our product range includes a variety of meats, from premium steaks and
        succulent roasts to fresh poultry and house-made sausages. Each product
        is crafted with care, ensuring you receive the best quality every time
        you shop with us.
      </p>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        We are also excited to offer a selection of marinades, rubs, and
        specialty items that pair perfectly with our meats, helping you elevate
        your culinary creations at home.
      </p>

      <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200">
        Join Us
      </h3>
      <p class="mb-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        We invite you to visit us at our shop to experience the quality and
        service that sets us apart. Whether you're looking for a special cut for
        a celebration or everyday essentials, our team is here to help. Don’t
        hesitate to ask our knowledgeable staff for recommendations or cooking
        tips—we’re here to make your meat shopping experience enjoyable and
        informative.
      </p>
      <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400">
        Stay connected with us on social media for updates on new products,
        special offers, and events. Join our growing community of meat lovers
        and discover the difference that quality makes.
      </p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
